image package for @TARGET_TRIPLE@

Target kind: @TARGET_KIND@

Components:
- libjpeg-turbo @LIBJPEG_TURBO_VERSION@
- libpng @LIBPNG_VERSION@
- libtiff @LIBTIFF_VERSION@

This prefix is layered on top of postgresql_dependencies for the same target.
It intentionally does not contain GDAL, GEOS, PROJ, SpatiaLite, PostgreSQL,
libpq, or pg_config.
